            {
              "text" : ".",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "To further configure an attachable value before you attach it, use it to",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "initialize an instance of ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/org.swift.testing\/documentation\/Testing\/Attachment",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " and set its properties before",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "passing it to ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/org.swift.testing\/documentation\/Testing\/Attachment\/record(_:sourceLocation:)",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : ". An attachable",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "value can only be attached to a test once.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "A type can conform to this protocol if it represents another type that",
